    <body>
        <p>Select the <span class="Emphasis">Columns</span> tab. Then create columns by typing a label in the text box and pressing <b>ENTER</b> or clicking <img src="../../../Images/Central/Interface/Buttons/Add-btn2.png" alt="" title="" class="ReduceButtonSize" />. Repeat this for each column you want to add. You can use the up and down arrows to change the order of the columns (the column at the top of the dialog will appear at the far left in the checklist, and the column at the bottom will appear at the far right).</p>
    </body>
</html>